#| "Use the <guilabel>Find Object</guilabel> window (<keycombo action=\"simul"
#| "\">&Ctrl;<keycap>F</keycap></keycombo>) to locate Polaris. Notice that "
#| "its Declination is almost (but not exactly) +90 degrees. Compare the "
